Organizations.Name: Atom
Organizations.Description: Atom was a group development solutions organization based off of the Roblox platform. Atom's primary objective was to provide group ranking services to hundreds of groups accross Roblox
Organizations.Note: The entirety of Atom was coded by myself and contains its own custom framework, content-delivery system, and secure token system.

Organizations.Name: Vanguard Servers
Organizations.Description: Vanguard Servers was a Garry's Mod based server community that relied heavily on its custom content to provide its players with unique experiences. All custom content seen on the server network was created using the Lua programming language.
Organizations.Note: This organization has no direct connection to Roblox based development besides the use of Lua as the primary programming langauge.

Groups.Name: The Nova Corporation
Groups.Description: The Nova Corportation is a unique anomalous entity contaimment roleplay group that has the best of the best development and community on Roblox!
Groups.Note: This is my favorite group on Roblox!

Groups.Name: The Euphoria Project
Groups.Description: The Euphoria Project is my own development studio that houses numerous different projects & games. Most notably the game, In The City which has yet to release.
Groups.Note: This group is listed as featured because of its use of my own custom game framework and displays my current skill level, having inter-server communication and Roblox -> VPS communication.

Groups.Name: Code Red Community
Groups.Description: Code Red was a multi-map, round based, survival & combat game. The goal of the player will vary based on their given class, and each class will have an end objective. Every player has the chance and ability to win if they play to their strengths and outsmart the other players.

Groups.Name: Special Containment Procedures Foundation
Groups.Description: The SCP Foundation is a fictional organization documented by the web-based collaborative-fiction project of the same name. The SCP Foundation is responsible for locating and containing individuals, entities, locations, and objects that violate natural law
Groups.Note: This is not a full-time position and is treated more as a in-house contractor position.

Groups.Name: Foxtrot Asylum Roleplay
Groups.Description: The Foxtrot Medical Institute is a mental asylum that is committed to concealment of the mentally ill as well as the maintenance of order and a safe environment.

Groups.Name: United States Army
Groups.Description: The United States Army is the land warfare service branch of the United States Armed Forces. It is the most senior and largest branch of the Armed Forces. The origins of the U.S. Army can be traced back to the Revolutionary War.

Groups.Name: United States Μarine Cοrps
Groups.Description: The United States Marine Corps is a branch of the U.S. Military responsible for providing power projection, using the mobility of the Navy, by Congressional mandate, to deliver rapidly, combined-arms task forces on land, at sea, and in the air.

Groups.Name: United States Air Force
Groups.Description: The United States Air Force (USAF) is the aerial warfare service branch of the United States Armed Forces. Initially formed as a part of the United States Army on 1 August 1907, the USAF was established as a separate branch of the U.S. Armed Forces on 18 September 1947.

Projects.Name: Facility Bravo
Projects.Description: Facility Bravo was a roleplay facility tasked with containing new viruses and diseases, as well as the treatment of people infected with these.

Projects.Name: Speed Simulator
Projects.Description: Speed Simulator is a game designed around increasing your speed through the use of various activites such as consuming drinks, jumping over obstacles, and participating in races..

Projects.Name: Area-39 Roleplay
Projects.Description: Area-39 is an SCP Roleplay game where you can pick and choose from a variety of teams and unlock those teams by playing the game.

Projects.Name: The Quarantine
Projects.Description: The Quarantine was a post-apocolyptic game centered around a future where the United States is in ruins. It focuses on the dangerous passage to saftey and crossing borders.
